name: Hoth: Ice Plains (5th Marker) (V)
LocationDStext: Once per game, may take a non-[Maintenance] AT-AT into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. During your move phase, may move for free between here and Mountains.
LocationLStext: If Imperial Control on table, add one [Light Side Force] here and at Mountains. Ice Storm, Rebel Base Occupation, and opponent's Colo Claw Fish are canceled.
